  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Become the Fear</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Taram Baba is an <strong>Action Roguelike</strong> that focuses on <strong>lightning-fast combat</strong> mechanics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3420790/extras/591e67c3d893e14ecdcab36db76cefae.poster.avif?t=1774443510\" width=800 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3420790/extras/591e67c3d893e14ecdcab36db76cefae.webm?t=1774443510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3420790/extras/591e67c3d893e14ecdcab36db76cefae.mp4?t=1774443510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fight Your Way</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feel every blow you land on evil while you fight your way through the haunting abyss. Chase Taram Baba deeper and deeper into the dark and cling to your light, for the walls are moving.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3420790/extras/ffec3e6a3ad681d9bb2ec8307f7eca3c.avif?t=1774443510\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3420790/extras_big/ffec3e6a3ad681d9bb2ec8307f7eca3c.avif?t=1774443510 width=800 height=336 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Taram Baba focuses on responsive, lightning-fast, satisfying combat. From the variety of Dead Cells to the juicy hits of Scourgebringer, from the atmosphere of Hollow Knight to the speed of Katana Zero, it blends many elements to create a spectacular action feast.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique level generation algorithm that regenerates every place you have passed through, enhances the fever dream experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3420790/extras/31b928c82b8f8dd22a5048c39a57d3fe.avif?t=1774443510\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3420790/extras_big/31b928c82b8f8dd22a5048c39a57d3fe.avif?t=1774443510 width=800 height=396 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Become the Fear</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Taram Baba is an <strong>Action Roguelike</strong> that focuses on <strong>lightning-fast combat</strong> mechanics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3420790/extras/591e67c3d893e14ecdcab36db76cefae.poster.avif?t=1774443510\" width=800 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3420790/extras/591e67c3d893e14ecdcab36db76cefae.webm?t=1774443510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3420790/extras/591e67c3d893e14ecdcab36db76cefae.mp4?t=1774443510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fight Your Way</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feel every blow you land on evil while you fight your way through the haunting abyss. Chase Taram Baba deeper and deeper into the dark and cling to your light, for the walls are moving.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3420790/extras/ffec3e6a3ad681d9bb2ec8307f7eca3c.avif?t=1774443510\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3420790/extras_big/ffec3e6a3ad681d9bb2ec8307f7eca3c.avif?t=1774443510 width=800 height=336 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Taram Baba focuses on responsive, lightning-fast, satisfying combat. From the variety of Dead Cells to the juicy hits of Scourgebringer, from the atmosphere of Hollow Knight to the speed of Katana Zero, it blends many elements to create a spectacular action feast.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique level generation algorithm that regenerates every place you have passed through, enhances the fever dream experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3420790/extras/31b928c82b8f8dd22a5048c39a57d3fe.avif?t=1774443510\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3420790/extras_big/31b928c82b8f8dd22a5048c39a57d3fe.avif?t=1774443510 width=800 height=396 /></span></p>",
